#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "2,000 parents<br/> brought their kid to our nursery."
msgstr "2.000 Eltern<br/> haben ihr Kind unserem Kindergarten anvertraut."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        For every kid"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Für jedes Kind"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Open-door policy"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Politik der offenen Tür"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Our mission"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Unsere Missio"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid "A little place <br/>of paradise"
msgstr "Ein kleines <br/>Paradies"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "About us"
msgstr "Über uns"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "Aktivitäten"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"All activities are planned to meet each child’s individual needs. This "
"approach will help your child to develop to the best of their ability."
msgstr ""
"Alle Aktivitäten werden so geplant, dass die individuellen Bedürfnissen "
"jedes Kindes erfüllt werden. Dieser Ansatz wird Ihrem Kind helfen, sich "
"bestmöglich zu entwickeln."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Contact us"
msgstr "Kontaktieren Sie uns"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_kiddo.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Anzeigename"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Entrust us with your children and go to work with peace of mind"
msgstr "Vertrauen Sie uns Ihre Kinder an und gehen Sie unbesorgt zur Arbeit"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Events"
msgstr "Veranstaltungen"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_kiddo.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Our aim is to make the early years of your child’s life as enjoyable, "
"rewarding and positive as possible."
msgstr ""
"Unser Ziel ist es, die ersten Jahre im Leben Ihres Kindes so unterhaltsam, "
"angenehm und positiv wie möglich zu gestalten."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid ""
"Our goal is to create a safe and nurturing environment for your child to "
"learn and grow. We believe that every child is unique and should be treated "
"as such."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Our team"
msgstr "Unser Team"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Our team is composed of experienced nursery nurses."
msgstr "Unser Team besteht aus erfahrenen Kindergärtnern."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Playground"
msgstr "Spielplatz"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_kiddo.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Designwerkzeuge"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid ""
"They will propose to your children educational activities, playful, varied "
"and adapted to the stage of development."
msgstr ""
"Sie werden Ihren Kindern pädagogische Aktivitäten vorschlagen, die "
"spielerisch, abwechslungsreich und an den Entwicklungsstand angepasst sind."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Visit us"
msgstr "Besuchen Sie uns"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"You are welcome to come and see the nursery and meet the team at any time "
"convenient to you."
msgstr ""
"Sie sind herzlich eingeladen, unseren Kindergarten zu besichtigen und das "
"Team kennenzulernen, wann immer es Ihnen passt."

#. module: theme_kiddo
